00073     private Vector _elements;
00074     private boolean readonly;
00075         
00076     public CViolation() {  
00077         setReadOnly(false);
00078         _elements = new Vector(ELEMENT_COUNT);
00079         for (int i = 0; i < _elements.capacity(); ++i) 
00080         {
00081                 // initialize with current date-time values
00082                 if (i == DATE || i == TIME || i == BAC_DATE || i == BAC_TIME) 
00083                 {
00084                         Date date = new Date(System.currentTimeMillis());
00085                         _elements.addElement(date.toString());
00086                 }
00087                 else 
00088                 {
00089                         _elements.addElement(new String(""));
00090                 }
00091         }
00092     }
00093 
00099     public String getElement(int id) {
00100         
00101         // provide parameter guard check
00102         if (id < 0 || id >= ELEMENT_COUNT ) return null;
00103         
00104         return (String) _elements.elementAt(id);
00105     }
00106 
00107     
00114     public void setElement(int id, String value) {
00115         
00116         // provide parameter guard check
00117         if (id < 0 || id >= ELEMENT_COUNT ) return;
00118 
00119         if (!isReadOnly()) {
00120                 _elements.setElementAt(value, id);
00121         }
00122     }
